1: -module(cache_server_SUITE).
    2: 
    3: -compile(export_all).
    4: 
    5: -include_lib("eunit/include/eunit.hrl").
    6: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
    7: 
    8: all() -> [
    9:     test_start_link
   10: ].
   11: 
   12: 
   13: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   14:     Config.
   15: 
   16: init_per_testcase(test_start_link, Config) ->
   17:     Test1 = #{
   18:             <<"table_name">> => a,
   19:             <<"drop_interval">> => 5
   20:     },
   21:     [{<<"start_link">>, Test1} | Config].
   22: 
   23: end_per_testcase(test_start_link, Config) ->
   24:     Config.
   25: 
   26: end_per_suite(Config) ->
   27:     Config.
   28: 
   29: 
   30: test_start_link(Config) ->
   31:     Map = proplists:get_value(<<"start_link">>, Config),
   32:     TableName = maps:get(<<"table_name">>, Map),
   33:     DropInterval = maps:get(<<"drop_interval">>, Map),    
   34:     ?_assertEqual(
   35:         ok, ok
   36:         %%cache_server:start_link(TableName, [{drop_interval, DropInterval}])
   37:     ).
